```hcl
# Enforce IMDSv2 on an EC2 instance
resource "aws_instance" "<example_resource_name>" {
  ami           = "<example_resource_id>"
  instance_type = "<example_resource_name>"

  metadata_options {
    http_tokens = "required"  # Critical: Require IMDSv2 tokens (blocks IMDSv1)
  }
}
```

```hcl
# Enforce IMDSv2 on an EC2 instance
